com.misc.common.moplaf.time.discrete

Interface BucketIterator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<TimeBucket>

    public interface BucketIterator
extends java.util.Iterator<TimeBucket>
    A representation of the model object 'PO Time Scale Iterator'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Bucket
    • From Date
    • To Date
    • Seconds
    • Is Before First
    • Is After Last
    • Is Valid
    • Part From Date
    • Part To Date
    • Part Seconds
    • Part In This
    • Time Scale
